[[Captain/Legends|Captain]] '''Prue''' was a member of the military of [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]]. He was an older man, with an academic bearing. He reported to [[Montross (bounty hunter)|Montross]] and [[General/Legends|General]] [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] that the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] force of [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Stardestroyers]] apparently moving toward [[Anchorhead/Legends|Anchorhead]] were in the completely wrong direction to be threatening the [[Aquilaean system]].

Nonetheless, Skywalker ordered the Aquilaean forces put on high alert. Prue later believed that the [[Death Star/Legends|space fortress]] was too huge to be an artificial body. When it vanishes for a time, Prue reported on this to the General. He later suggested that the Empire was jamming their communications to [[King/Legends|King]] [[Kayos]] as the royal convoy traveled to [[Amsel]].

He was presumably killed when the [[Underground Fortress]] was destroyed by [[nuclear bomb]]s set off by the Aquilaeans to prevent an Imperial capture of their precious biological science.

